==Standard dialogue==
===Elven city guard===
* {{tbox|He's standing deadly still and not responding to any attempt you make to distract or talk to him.}}

===Party Pete===
* '''Player:''' Why oh why am I not surprise to see you here.{{sic}}
* '''Player:''' I don't recall anything you've one{{sic}} over the past year?
* '''Party Pete:''' If there's a party, I'm there!
* '''Player:''' Enjoy yourself then.
* {{tact|end}}

===Nieve===
* '''Player:''' Nieve? What a surprise!
* '''Player:''' Wh...why have you brought a Cave Kraken with you?
* '''Nieve:''' Oh this one's harmless. It seems to have a habit of following me everytime I enter my slayer dungeon to rescue yet another fool who thought they could finish that final slayer monster with no food and low HP.
* '''Nieve:''' So I figured I'd bring it along... it's kind of cute really.
* '''Player:''' If you say so...
* '''Nieve:''' Besides, it's not just this Kraken who's greatful{{sic}} to be here, I am too. The community wanted a kraken in game and the Old School team delivered. Without them, neither of us would be here.
* '''Player:''' I guess that's true. I hope you enjoy yourself!
* '''Nieve:''' Oh I shall, I like parties!
* {{tbox|The cave kraken stares blankly at you.}}
* {{tact|end}}

===High Priest===
* '''Player:''' You're not here to ruin and raid this event are you....?
* '''High Priest:''' Stupid human. Goblins love da' cake stuffs.
* '''Player:''' Well...errr...have fun!!
* {{tact|end}}

===Wise Old Man===
* '''Player:''' Taking a break from robbing banks to indludge{{sic}} in some partying and cake, are we?
* '''Wise Old Man:''' It would have been rude for the hosts of this party not to invite me.
* '''Player:''' Well, we haven't really seen much of you over the past year.
* '''Player:''' What entitles you to be recognised here?
* '''Wise Old Man:''' Oh, I'm occasionally hearing reports of some of the developers transmogrifying into a form, similar to myself, and then parading around as me.
* '''Wise Old Man:''' So I figured, since i'm{{sic}} important enough to frankly have my identity stolen, then I'm important enough to be present here.
* '''Player:''' Touché{{sic}}
* '''Wise Old Man:''' Besides, this is a gangsta's paradice{{sic}} and the women appreciate a man with my level of styleee.{{sic}}
* '''Player:''' I'll leave you too it.
* {{tbox|The Wise old{{sic}} Man starts to bust a move. I hope it{{sic}} doesn't bust a hip...}}
* {{tact|end}}

===Doomsayer===
* '''Doomsayer:''' IT'S DYING! IT'S ALL DYING! THE GAME IS DYING!!
* '''Player:''' .....................................................
* '''Player:''' Who even invited you.....
* {{tact|end}}

===Dominic Onion===
* '''Player:''' Dominic? What're you doing here?
* '''Dominic Onion:''' I figured I'd come and pay my birthday respects to the team that invented me. I wasn't around in the original 2007 game and if it wasn't for them, I may never of{{sic}} existed!
* '''Player:''' I see you brought your trusty....steed.
* '''Dominic Onion:''' I figured I'd let the ol' girl out for a bit. Those darn boosters kept hitting her whilst they were in the lobby area. Poor girl...
* {{tact|end}}

===BigRedJapan===
* '''Player:''' Taking a break from shouting at people on rooftops eh, Japan?
* '''BigRedJapan:''' I figured everyone got tired of me shouting my name at them everytime they tried to do a lap and it's a party, 'course I'm going to attend!
* '''Player:''' You're not wrong there.
* '''Player:''' Hope you have fun!
* {{tact|end}}

===Anti-Santa===
* '''Player:''' Happy Birthday Sa...I mean Anti-Santa!
* '''Anti-Santa:''' This is the worst event I have ever seen. Where's the chaos? Where's the misery?
* '''Player:''' Pot of joy you are....
* {{tact|end}}

===Lumbridge Guide===
====In Prifddinas====
* '''Lumbridge Guide:''' Hello, adventurer! Welcome to the party!
* '''Player:''' Party? What party?
* '''Lumbridge Guide:''' Why.. it's Old School RuneScape's first birthday! A year ago everything we see now was reanimated for this very community.
* '''Player:''' Sweet! I better go and celebrate!
* '''Lumbridge Guide:''' Go ahead adventurer. I'm sure those responsible for this dream world would want you to be enjoying yourself.
* '''Player:''' I shall! I really am appreciative of all their hard work. 
* '''Player:''' And I'm saying that off my own back and am in no way being forced into saying so....Really!
* {{tact|end}}

====Right-click leave option at the Lumbridge Guide====
* '''Player:''' I'd like to leave please.
* '''Lumbridge Guide:''' Are you sure? I mean...there's a huge cake here and you've no doubt wanted to get into this place for years. Why leave?
* {{tselect|Are you sure you want to leave?}}
* {{topt|Yes}}
** '''Player:''' *sigh*
** '''Player:''' Yes please. I can always come back later.
** '''Lumbridge Guide:''' Alright, here goes.
** {{qact|The player is teleported to Lumbridge.}}
* {{topt|No}}
** '''Player:''' Actually, you're right.
** '''Player:''' I'll go and mingle amongst all those ankou.
** '''Player:''' They really are everywhere....
** {{tact|end}}

====Speaking to the Lumbridge Guide at Lumbridge====
* '''Lumbridge Guide:''' Greetings, adventurer. I am Phileas, the Lumbridge Guide. I am here to give information and directions to new players. Do you require any help?
* {{tselect|Select an Option}}
* {{topt|Yes please.|event=no}}
* {{topt|No, I can find things myself thank you.|event=no}}
* {{topt|Can you teleport me to Prifddinas?}}
** '''Lumbridge Guide:''' Sure, adventurer!
** '''Lumbridge Guide:''' Are you ready to go?
** {{tselect|Do you wish to go now?}}
** {{topt|Yes}}
*** '''Player:''' Yes!
*** {{qact|The player is teleported to Prifddinas.}}
** {{topt|No}}
